14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
16 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 295 of Title 17, unless there is
17 created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
18 As used in this act:
19 1. “Certificate of authority” means authorization for a
20 transmission developer by an order of the Corporation Commission
21 through filing of a case with an application, notice, and hearing.
22 The Corporation Commission shall establish a specific electric
23 transmission facility docket for the filing of such cases;
24
